APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW

2010-1660. State v. Palmer.

Franklin App. Nos. 09AP-956 and 09AP-957, 2010-Ohio-2421.

O’Connor, C.J., would accept the appeal on Proposition of Law Nos. I and II only and hold the cause for the decision in 2009-0088, State v. Williams, Warren App. No. CA2008-02-029, 2008-Ohio-6195.

Lundberg Stratton and Cupp, JJ., would also hold the cause for the decision in 2009-0088, State v. Williams.
